No. D-2736. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 4, 2013.

In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Jacob Addington ROSE.

Jacob Addington Rose, of West Palm Beach, Florida, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be *555disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
